      <title>美国全国一半军事基地位于“医疗荒漠”</title>
      <link>https://www.npr.org/2024/06/17/g-s1-4187/military-bases-shortage-health-care-troops-army-navy-marines</link>
      <description><![CDATA[对于数十万美国军人和他们的家人来说，当五角大楼命令他们到基地外寻求医疗服务时，他们却得不到任何医疗服务。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.npr.org/2024/06/17/g-s1-4187/military-bases-shortage-health-care-troops-army-navy-marines</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 17 Jun 2024 09:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
